Valid dictionary word that satisfies the constraints: “ELITE”.

- E is now in position 1 (a new spot; previously 4 & 5)  
- L is in position 2 (new spot; previously only 2)  
- I is in position 3 (same as before, but acceptable since we still need it somewhere)  
- T is a new high-frequency consonant  
- E is repeated here, but we have no restriction against double letters yet and it helps confirm E at a new index.
